Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.29,0:04:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来要拍摄选拔会  你一直期待的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要选拔我的妹妹  好难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全靠「天气少女  小魔女嘉音」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.44,0:04:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粉丝里增加了好多小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去淋个浴吧  好孩子的伙伴也得注意身体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:22.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  我也想参加嘉音妹妹的选拔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  之前要先通过资料筛选
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你看起来跟嘉音差不多大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差得远了  我比她大大约三百岁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.28,0:04:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请拿好资料进去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是  没有资料的人禁止进入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早知如此就多请教一下神哥哥关于妹属性了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.22,0:05:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请放手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  都说不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是没有宿主的落单驱魂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许在寻找寄宿的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.05,0:05:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得赶紧捉住它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(490.909,77.5758)\frz-10\1c000000\3cFFFFFF}艺人淋浴间\N无关人员禁止进入
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.73,0:05:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好小！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用羽衣帮你盖上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.16,0:06:59.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  我还以为驱魂寄宿到嘉音身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是嘉音…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎么看  我都变成小孩子了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.35,0:07:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办哦  艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下来还有工作  还要参加妹妹选拔会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.39,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冈田小姐还吩咐过我要注意身体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一下子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忽然地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唐突地
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就变成小孩的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静一下  嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.63,0:07:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音的危机就交给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部交给我解决吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.75,0:07:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  我该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要问我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不干  这回的目标是驱魂本体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不正是你擅长的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还想我干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.75,0:08:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正进行着一场不能输的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音之所以会变小
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正常来说都是因为驱魂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用你的驱魂探测器把它找出来  捉住它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉住施法后的驱魂  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次换你来排队！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  我来让嘉音变回…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.72,0:08:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去哪里了  嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(56.25,84.8485)\fs24.2424\1cE0CBFF\3c8F78BC}中川嘉音\N妹妹选拔会\N会场在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无意中就溜出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.16,0:09:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗  这里除了有关人员是不能进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有大人在身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.02,0:09:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.88,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.57,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟嘉音就像是一个模子里出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的真的好像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为就是本人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  你是来参加妹妹选拔的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才穿成这样  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:43.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  跟我一起过去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带你过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.64,0:09:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参加我自己的妹妹选拔？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹你叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中川…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:02.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…真音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真音？连名字都这么像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(347.727,60.6061)\fs24.2424\1cBEC6E4\3c0D88F0}中川嘉音\N妹妹选拔会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好豪华
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看  这根缎带跟嘉音的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.06,0:10:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像嘉音啊  真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:23.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻烦了  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.53,0:10:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一模一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太惊人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…其实  我不像你们那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有  那根缎带也很适合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.22,0:10:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真像嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  我很喜欢嘉音  能听你这么说好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:11:02.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢  所以很期待今天能见到嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.28,0:11:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成这副模样…该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音要出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能  我就在这里啊  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:23.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:24.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  是嘉音
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.63,0:11:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  为什么我会在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.99,0:11:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音她真的会魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.14,0:11:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气少女  小魔女嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每周星期天  绝赞播放中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天一定是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子  以为我就是电视剧里的那个小魔女嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是那么闪闪动人  会魔法也不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然时间表排得满满的  不过接下小魔女的工作实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是现在这个状况该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那女生是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.91,0:12:28.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两个嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.16,0:12:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请把手机电源关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.74,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魂探测器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手机请关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是手机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:13:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那边那个嘉音整个就是一个假…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  你不能进里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我进去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中川嘉音  妹妹选拔会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别审查员当然就是这位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在嘉音面前能不能好好说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.06,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了  嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了  有两个我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是假的  是驱魂变的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魂？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家有危险  我们去通知她们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魂肯定是想装成嘉音去找间隙最大的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24.2424}（嘉音请评论）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪  她跟平时不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.78,0:14:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  接下来是小梢  有请
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了  假货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  请不要被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.67,0:14:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子才是真正的嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边真材实料的嘉音你们都不放在眼里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不行的  艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在还是小孩的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有些能确实证明是我自己的证据的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证据？  我的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:19.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算变成这样  唯独歌声…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你有完没完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的歌迷小妹妹们是为了见我才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要装成我  让她们伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:15:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得抓住它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小梢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24.2424\fnDFGMaruGothic-Lt}何も聞こえない  喧騒のなかで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩盖一切声息的喧嚣之中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救我  小魔女嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.82,0:16:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肯定是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.52,0:17:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也变成小孩子了  可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希  歌迷小妹妹们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  不赶快去救她们的话事情就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以这样  那我该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱歌  嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候驱魂对嘉音的歌有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魂是负能量  用嘉音的歌的正能量去冲击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会变弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请嘉音用你的歌去把那坏东西打倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用歌去打倒？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs24.2424\fnDFGMaruGothic-Lt}何も聞こえない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩盖一切声息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就算是在梦里面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的歌迷必须由我来保护
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变身成小魔女嘉音了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我绝对会把大家救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也得快点去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为在梦里面所以能飞起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.65,0:18:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.41,0:18:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小魔女嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来做你对手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.32,0:18:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个坏东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.51,0:19:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的歌把你打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女生是嘉音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  加油啊  嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱魂拘留
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.78,0:20:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了  嘉音  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愿明日天晴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.93,0:20:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.31,0:21:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒过来发现大家都睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.02,0:21:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部人都睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.11,0:21:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾露希
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:19.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊  果然是梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.47,0:21:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音果然会用魔法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安无事抓住驱魂实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来嘉音好帅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后不找神哥哥  找嘉音帮忙抓驱魂好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这驱魂好像有什么不够的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道还没抓完
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.99,0:22:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次轮到我变成小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.80,0:22:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.74,0:22:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中川嘉音妹妹选拔会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优胜者是小梢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.91,0:22:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜  小梢  今天开始作为我的妹妹多多指教啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘉音我好开心
